<p data-sourcepos="4:1-4:178" dir="auto">Arcadia is the Git server of the HardLOG Research Group. Powered by <a href="https://gitlab.com/" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" target="_blank">GitLab</a>, this tool helps us build the algorithms and tools for our educational and research projects.</p>
<p data-sourcepos="6:1-6:18" dir="auto">Arcadia lets you:</p>
<ul data-sourcepos="7:1-10:0" dir="auto">
<li data-sourcepos="7:1-7:87">Manage Git repositories with fine-grained access controls that keep your code secure.</li>
<li data-sourcepos="8:1-8:69">Perform code reviews and enhance collaboration with merge requests.</li>
<li data-sourcepos="9:1-10:0">Easily setup a an issue tracker and a wiki for each project.</li>
